00:07:18.459 --> 00:07:24.459
Let's hear from some brothers who have worked in the field for many years and see what we can learn.

00:07:24.459 --> 00:07:31.459
Meet Nick Aladis, Nick XRKs and Saki Moray.

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:43.120
